title: 1973 - Cotter - Dired by Paul Stanley UNCENSORED

sources.title: 1973 - Cotter - Dired by Paul Stanley UNCENSORED
sources.description:
Alkoholic rodeo clown Cotter fails to save a rider from an enraged bull. Depressed, he returns to his home town. When a rancher is found dead a lynch mob set out to kill the 'drunken Indian.'

Director: Paul Stanley
Writer: William D. Gordon
Stars: Don Murray, Carol Lynley, Rip Torn

Genres: Drama, Western

aka The Narrow Chute
